  * Add Latvian translation

  [ Daniel Rusek ]
  * emergency-call-types: Add Czech Republic

  [ Piotr Drąg ]
  * Update Polish translation

  [ Athmane MOKRAOUI ]
  * Add Kabyle translation

 -- Guido Günther <agx@sigxcpu.org>  Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:41:16 +0100

